init_text: All of the "#1 Dad" mugs in the world change to show the actual ranking of Dads suddenly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: His son asked him if that was accurate.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He wished that his son did not notice.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "I'm just going to set that on a different shelf."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "Listen, son, I may not be a great dad.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: His son looked at the mug.
